snippet.description:
#KMJS na!

Tumutok na sa inyong telebisyon at sa ating livestream!

Narito ang mga kuwentong tampok namin ngayong gabi:

HINOSTAGE SA JEEP | MUKBANGAN SA DALAMPASIGAN | CHRONIC KIDNEY DISEASE RISING | JILLIAN MULTIVERSE | SA SIPIT NG BATAS AT KATARUNGAN | BANTAY SA ILOG NG AKLAN 

Tumutok sa ating programa at maki-tweet sa amin mamaya gamit ang ating official hashtag: #KMJS.

"Kapuso Mo, Jessica Soho" (One at Heart, Jessica Soho) is the Philippines' top-rating news magazine program, hosted by one of the most-awarded broadcast journalists in the country, Jessica Soho. snippet.title: JAZZ at LAKERS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | February 10, 2025
snippet.description:
The Lakers defeated the Jazz, 132-113 tonight in Los Angeles. LeBron James contributed a team-high 24 points to go with 8 assists 7 rebounds and 3 three pointers, with Austin Reaves of the Lakers adding an additional 22 points (6-10 FG, 3-5 3P), 9 rebounds, and 4 assists in the game. Lauri Markkanen finished with a team-high 17 points along with 3 rebounds for the Jazz in the losing effort. The Lakers improve their record to 32-19 with the win, while the Jazz fall to 12-40 for the season. The teams will meet again in their next game on Wednesday, 2/12/2025, when the Jazz host the Lakers (9:00 PM ET, KJZZ/Spectrum SportsNet).
